Recordings
============================================================


A set of scripts for recording webradio.


setup.sh
---------

Generates everything that is needed for a new radio to be recorded.

A config file must be passed.

Project folder and subfolders.

Tests the stream and determines used codec.



record.sh
---------

Starts new recording.



cover.sh
---------

Generates artistic cover.


index.sh
--------

Generates html 5 page with audio players.


metadata.sh
-----------

Webcrawler. Template for providing custom metadata to streamripper.


sample.conf
-----------

Use this template when creating new config files for other radio stations. 




Dependencies
-------------

streamripper
mp3cut
AtomicParsley
EyeD3


 
